Insider Activity


Individual




Bernie W. Stewart



Mr. Bernie W. Stewart is Independent Class I Director at Hornbeck Offshore Services, Inc. (Louisiana). He is on the Board of Directors at Hornbeck Offshore Services, Inc. (Louisiana).
Mr. Stewart was previously employed as President by Falcon Drilling Co., Inc., President & Chief Operating Officer by R&B Falcon Holdings, Inc., Chief Operating Officer & Senior Vice President by Hornbeck Offshore Services, Inc., President by Western Oceanic, Inc., and Senior Vice President-Operations by R&B Falcon Corp.



